IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.qcparceldamagereport') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.qcparceldamagereport
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.qcparceldamagereport (

[id] int,
[parcelid] int,
[parcelbarcode] nvarchar(4000),
[billingcustomerid] int,
[billingcustomer] nvarchar(4000),
[auditbyid] int,
[auditby] nvarchar(4000),
[locationid] int,
[location] nvarchar(4000),
[date] datetime2(7),
[parcelweightkg] float,
[parcelwidthcm] numeric(36,6),
[parcellengthcm] numeric(36,6),
[parcelheightcm] numeric(36,6),
[volumiserweight] numeric(36,6),
[volumiserlengthcm] numeric(36,6),
[volumiserheightcm] numeric(36,6),
[volumiserwidthcm] numeric(36,6),
[auditquantity] int,
[auditweight] numeric(36,6),
[flutemeasure] numeric(36,6),
[shrinkwrap] int,
[comment] nvarchar(4000),
[utilization] nvarchar(4000),
[missing] int,
[damaged] int,
[flutedescription] nvarchar(4000),
[tapetype] nvarchar(4000),


	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/RPT/qcparceldamagereport.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.qcparceldamagereport
GO
